# Safety Considerations
safety_considerations: |
  This pack involves real tools and real danger. Parent/guardian permission required.
  Supervision by trained adult always required. PPE mandatory. Emergency procedures
  established. First aid available. All activities selected for age-appropriateness.
  No activities beyond what professional instructors would allow at given age level.

