# Notes for Implementers
implementation_notes: |
  Requires dedicated shop space with tools, materials, and workbenches. Instructor must
  have trades background or co-teach with practiced tradesperson. Budget for materials
  and tool maintenance. Build relationships with local tradespeople for mentorship and
  apprenticeship connections. Celebrate projects visibly — they matter.

